# 1. Purpose

This document provides low-fidelity wireframes for the Dealership Lead Management System implemented on Salesforce Automotive Cloud.

The wireframes represent the key screens required to support lead capture, assignment, qualification, test drive scheduling, opportunity management, and reporting.

These wireframes are intended to help business stakeholders, developers, QA teams, and solution architects understand the expected system functionality and user experience.

---

# Screen 1: Lead Management Dashboard

## Purpose

Provides sales representatives and managers with a consolidated view of lead activities, assignments, follow-ups, and performance metrics.

## Wireframe

```text
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
| DEALERSHIP LEAD MANAGEMENT DASHBOARD                        |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+

Total Leads: 1,245
Qualified Leads: 450
Converted Leads: 182
Conversion Rate: 14.6%

+-------------------------------------------------------------+
| My Assigned Leads                                           |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
| Lead ID | Customer | Vehicle | Status | Follow-Up Date     |
|-------------------------------------------------------------|
| LD001   | John D.  | SUV     | New    | 12-Jun-2026        |
| LD002   | Sarah K. | Sedan   | Contacted | 13-Jun-2026     |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+

+-------------------------------------------------------------+
| Upcoming Activities                                         |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
| Follow-Up Call - 10:00 AM                                   |
| Test Drive - 02:00 PM                                       |
| Customer Meeting - 04:00 PM                                 |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
```

## Functional Requirements

* Display lead summary metrics.
* Display assigned leads.
* Display upcoming tasks and reminders.
* Allow quick navigation to lead records.

